<template class="container_alert">
    <v-container >
        <v-alert 
            type="error"
            variant="tonal"
        >{{asset.name}} {{text}} {{text_increment}}</v-alert>
 
    </v-container>
  </template>
  
  <script>
    export default {
      name: 'PxAlert',
      data: () => ({
      }),
      props: {
//este cant lo recibo de paginacion.vue
    text: {
      default: "",
    },
    text_increment: {
      default: "",
    },
    asset: {
      default: {},
    },
  },

    }
  </script>
  <style>
.container_alert{
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
}
  </style>
